data.description: This home is on a corner lot just under an acre with double gates on both sides to access backyard. There is a covered carport to park your boat and a workshop with power and a 220 outlet. Inside you will find tile flooring throughout and the living, kitchen and dining is all open making it perfect for entertaining. The kitchen features a breakfast bar, granite counters and a pantry with pull out drawers. The large utility room has a sink and storage closet for cleaning supplies and plenty of room for more. This home has NEVER FLOODED!!!!Come check this one out before it's gone!
